.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-6::.
There 4 different types of food: pineapple, cauliflower, cucumber, avocado
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, skydiving, rock-climbing, dancing
4 different pets are kept: hedgehog, bird, cat, pony
1. the person eating cauliflower is in an odd position##4
2. the owner of the cat is on the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
3. the owner of the hedgehog is the person eating cauliflower##1
4. the person eating cucumber is on the left of the owner of the bird##1
5. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the far right##1
6. the person eating avocado is on the left of the person eating cauliflower##1
7. the person eating avocado is in an even position##4
8. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2      |     3      |    4    |
| Food    | cucumber   | avocado      | cauliflower       | pineapple |
| Hobby   | card-games | dancing | rock-climbing     | skydiving |
| Pet     | pony     | bird  | hedgehog | cat |

