.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-7::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, water, almond-milk, mirinda
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: superhero, epic, disaster, horror
4 different pets are kept: hedgehog, dog, goldfish, fish
1. the owner of the goldfish is the person watching superhero movies##1
2. the owner of the dog is between the person watching horror movies and the owner of the hedgehog##2
3. the person watching horror movies is the person drinking water##1
4. the person watching epic movies is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3
5. the person drinking cola is in an even position##4
6. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
7. the person watching superhero movies is the person drinking cola##1
8. the owner of the goldfish is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |       3       |     4      |
| Beverage      | almond-milk   | mirinda          | water | cola        |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster     | epic | horror   | superhero     |
| Pet           | hedgehog | dog         | fish         | goldfish |

