.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-8::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: puzzles, baking, rock-climbing, fishing
The people have 4 different jobs:  dancer, mechanic, security-guard, engineer
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: folk, dubstep, r&b, classical
1. the fan of classical is on the left or right of the fan of r&b##3
2. the security-guard is the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
3. the engineer is the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
4. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the fan of r&b##1
5. the fan of dubstep is between the dancer and the person who's hobby is puzzles##2
6. the fan of classical is on the left or right of the security-guard##3
7. the person who's hobby is puzzles is in an even position##4
8. the person who's hobby is puzzles is between the person who's hobby is baking and the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3       |     4      |
| Hobby         | baking | puzzles      | rock-climbing       | fishing    |
| Job           | mechanic  | security-guard  | engineer | dancer |
| Music-Genre   | classical      | r&b | dubstep         | folk    |

