.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-9::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, sprite, juice, soy-milk
The people have 4 different jobs:  librarian, electrician, security-guard, mechanic
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, soccer, biathlon, golf
1. the librarian is in an odd position##4
2. the person drinking lemonade is on the left or right of the librarian##3
3. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the librarian##3
4. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
5. the person drinking sprite is on the left or right of the person who's sport is biathlon##3
6. the person who's sport is golf is on the right of the librarian##1
7. the librarian is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
8. the electrician is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
9. the mechanic is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |      3       |       4       |
| Beverage   | sprite         | lemonade  | juice     | soy-milk         |
| Job        | mechanic | electrician | librarian | security-guard         |
| Sport      | soccer         | biathlon  | cycling   | golf |

