.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-10::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: r&b, house, techno, ambient
There are 4 different nationalities: chinese, american, pakistani, argentine
4 different pets are kept: ferret, goat, fish, rat
 1. the owner of the fish is on the left or right of the fan of techno##3
 2. the chinese is on the far left or far right##3
 3. the owner of the goat is on the right of the fan of house##1
 4. the pakistani is between the fan of house and the fan of r&b##2
 5. the owner of the rat is on the left or right of the fan of house##3
 6. the owner of the rat is the fan of techno##1
 7. the argentine is on the far right##1
 8. the fan of r&b is in an odd position##4
 9. the american is between the fan of ambient and the fan of techno##2
10. the owner of the fish is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Music-Genre   | r&b  | techno    | house | ambient    |
| Nationality   | chinese | pakistani | american  | argentine |
| Pet           | fish   | rat    | ferret        | goat   |

