.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-11::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: tea, hot-chocolate, mirinda, sprite
The people have 4 different jobs:  musician, engineer, nurse, police-officer
There are 4 different nationalities: mexican, malaysian, brazilian, chinese
1. the person drinking tea is on the far left or far right##3
2. the engineer is on the left of the musician##1
3. the chinese is on the left or right of the nurse##3
4. the engineer is in an even position##4
5. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the musician##1
6. the chinese is on the right of the engineer##1
7. the malaysian is on the left of the engineer##1
8. the person drinking sprite is on the left or right of the malaysian##3
9. the person drinking tea is on the left of the mexican##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |         1          |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Beverage      | tea                | sprite  | hot-chocolate | mirinda   |
| Job           | police-officer | engineer | musician   | nurse |
| Nationality   | malaysian         | mexican     | chinese     | brazilian |

