.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-12::.
There 4 different types of food: onion, apricot, cabbage, artichoke
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: superhero, spy, documentary, disaster
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, rock, metal, hip-hop
1. the person eating apricot is on the left of the person eating artichoke##1
2. the person eating cabbage is on the far left##1
3. the fan of rock is on the left or right of the fan of hip-hop##3
4. the person eating cabbage is on the left of the person watching spy movies##1
5. the fan of blues is between the person watching disaster movies and the fan of hip-hop##2
6. the person watching documentary movies is in an even position##4
7. the person eating onion is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |   3    |    4    |
| Food          | cabbage    | apricot  | artichoke  | onion |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster | spy | superhero | documentary |
| Music-Genre   | metal    | blues     | hip-hop    | rock |

