.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-13::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, soy-milk, lemonade, cola
There are 4 different nationalities: mexican, german, japanese, canadian
4 different pets are kept: lizard, guinea-pig, rabbit, cat
1. the owner of the guinea-pig is between the person drinking lemonade and the mexican##2
2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the far left or far right##3
3. the japanese is on the left or right of the owner of the rabbit##3
4. the owner of the cat is on the left of the german##1
5. the owner of the cat is in an odd position##4
6. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the owner of the rabbit##3
7. the mexican is on the left or right of the canadian##3
8. the japanese is the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
9. the canadian is between the owner of the rabbit and the owner of the lizard##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3    |     4     |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate | lemonade      | soy-milk  | cola    |
| Nationality   | japanese   | german | canadian | mexican |
| Pet           | cat      | rabbit       | guinea-pig   | lizard      |

