.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-14::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: fishing, cooking, gardening, baking
There are 4 different nationalities: canadian, mexican, chinese, dutch
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skiing, rugby, rowing, tennis
1. the person who's hobby is gardening is in an even position##4
2. the person who's hobby is cooking is between the person who's hobby is baking and the person who's sport is skiing##2
3. the person who's sport is rugby is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person who's hobby is baking is in an even position##4
5. the person who's sport is skiing is on the right of the person who's sport is rowing##1
6. the dutch is between the person who's sport is skiing and the canadian##2
7. the person who's sport is rugby is on the far right##1
8. the mexican is in an even position##4
9. the person who's sport is skiing is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |    3     |     4      |
| Hobby         | fishing    | gardening | cooking  | baking  |
| Nationality   | chinese | mexican       | dutch | canadian |
| Sport         | rowing   | skiing      | tennis | rugby       |

