.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-16::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, 7up, hot-chocolate, coffee
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, lacrosse, snowboarding, ice-hockey
The people use 4 different means of transport: taxi, quad-bike, train, boat
1. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the person drinking 7up##3
2. the person who's sport is basketball is in an even position##4
3. the person driving the boat is on the far left##1
4. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left or right of the person drinking coffee##3
5. the person drinking 7up is between the person driving the quad-bike and the person who's sport is snowboarding##2
6. the person driving the taxi is the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
7. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
8. the person who's sport is basketball is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Beverage    | hot-chocolate    | 7up     | soy-milk    | coffee        |
| Sport       | snowboarding   | basketball | lacrosse | ice-hockey |
| Transport   | boat | train      | quad-bike    | taxi   |

