3. the fan of ambient is on the far left##1
4. the fan of ambient is on the left of the fan of pop##1
5. the person watching drama movies is the indian##1
6. the fan of dubstep is on the right of the thai##1
7. the thai is on the right of the person watching thriller movies##1
8. the fan of ambient is on the left of the person watching superhero movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |     3     |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller | superhero | drama | musical   |
| Music-Genre   | ambient    | pop   | dubstep     | r&b    |
| Nationality   | russian  | thai | indian  | polish |

