.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-20::.
There 4 different types of food: blueberry, pineapple, strawberry, grapes
The people have 4 different hobbies: writing, collecting, photography, gardening
4 different pets are kept: turtle, goldfish, cat, chinchilla
1. the person eating blueberry is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's hobby is gardening is in an odd position##4
3. the owner of the turtle is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is writing##3
4. the person eating strawberry is on the far left##1
5. the person eating pineapple is between the person who's hobby is gardening and the person who's hobby is writing##2
6. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left of the person who's hobby is writing##1
7. the owner of the cat is on the right of the person eating blueberry##1
8. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the person eating pineapple##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2      |   3    |      4      |
| Food    | strawberry    | pineapple    | blueberry  | grapes |
| Hobby   | gardening | collecting | writing | photography      |
| Pet     | goldfish   | turtle        | chinchilla   | cat       |

 